node.text:
A lot can be said for the growth I’ve had while starting school again, and while I feel like I can’t totally capture everything, here is a snippet of this new life. I love it here, and while it’s hard it is completely worth it and I know I’ve made the right decision to go get an art degree. 
Thanks to everyone for their kind words regarding the project, I’m very grateful for the support. :)

#potraits 
#gmitccam #contemporaryartgmit

Pansies and Payaras are available as a hand-done shirt made from block print. I’m excited to start working on more designs soon 

#gothart #darkartist  #linocutprint #tshirtart #blackandwhite #piranha
